  h1 Brandon and Ginger's Baby Shower Registry
  p We have already inherited many items from family and friends with slightly older children, and do not need much for the baby at this point.  However, we also know and appreciate how much you all want to help get us started on the best footing as parents!

  p If you plan on gifting, please do one of the following:
  ol
    li only purchase gifts that are on our registry,
    li contribute to a larger item, or
    li assist us in one of various ways as a gift.
  p More info on each below:

