  h2 Contributions
  p Here are a few higher-ticket items that we would love to have and are planning to invest in ourselves if/as needed.  Please talk to Sharon or Linda about contributing.
  ul
    li Rocking chair
    li College fund for the baby

  h2 Ways to Assist Us
  ul
    li A homemade meal, to be enjoyed with you at our home (so you can also meet the baby!).  We will have a sign-up sheet for this at the baby shower.
    li Gift card for #[a(href="http://backtobasicskitchen.com/products/gift-card") Back to Basics Kitchen].  These folks catered our wedding, and now make high-quality prepared foods that can be bought and warmed at home.
    li Subscription food services - if you’d like to contribute to one of these, please let Linda or Sharon know, and they coordinate it so we don’t get multiple of something all at once.  :-D
    ul
      li #[a(href='http://BlueApron.com') BlueApron.com]
      li #[a(href='http://LoveWithFood.com') LoveWithFood.com] (they give a meal to a hungry child with every box sent, and they have a gluten-free box!)
    li Time from a house-cleaning service
    li Other body- and/or soul-nourishing activities you can think of for us as new parents or for the whole family!
